Posts.Title: What a morning Also said I had 2 enlarges

Posts.Content: Well had my breast clinic appointment this morning. Lump prodded, mammogram amd ultrasound. They said it could be a cyst so drained it, dark red liquid. They then took 3 biopsies and said that the diagnosis is indeterminate. I am now worried again as at least a week more waiting. Feeling very unsettled at the moment. Also said I have 2 enlarged lymph nodes.
